race.comment: SPOILT ROTTEN (7) returns after a spell and started the last campaign in good style placing over 1100m at Toowoomba. He just missed there after as favourite and forget his latest when he was outgraded. Should be naturally improved and has found the right race. GEITZ (8) raced on the speed before fading to finish fourth last start when resuming over 1000m at Sunshine Coast. he will be fitter and has plenty up her sleeve. Has a wide gate to manage so she will need a good ride. The same goes for RUTHVEN RUSH (6), who looked a run short at Toowoomba first-up. Has the ability but will also have to do it the hard way. CAPTAIN BULL (2) has to be kept very safe on debut. Was an easy trial winner at Toowoomba and KWT will give him every chance from the inside gate. Elevate if the big money comes.
